{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01WtsVUcQ58WYKF9bh9PNVwk","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01EDBspcMgLodRgiyp5wnvnJ","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Refactor all Java files Spring->Quarkus","prompt":"I am migrating the DayTrader application from Spring Boot to Quarkus. The working directory is /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__spring__quarkus/run_1/output\n\nI need you to refactor ALL Java source files to replace Spring-specific annotations and patterns with Quarkus/CDI equivalents. Here are the specific changes needed for each file:\n\n**IMPORTANT: You MUST read each file before editing it.**\n\n## 1. DaytraderApplication.java\nReplace the entire file. In Quarkus, there's no main class needed (Quarkus provides its own). But we can keep a simple main class for io.quarkus.runtime.Quarkus.run():\n\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader;\n\nimport io.quarkus.runtime.Quarkus;\nimport io.quarkus.runtime.annotations.QuarkusMain;\n\n@QuarkusMain\npublic class DaytraderApplication {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        Quarkus.run(args);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## 2. ServletInitializer.java \nDELETE this file entirely (or make it empty). It's Spring-specific.\nReplace with:\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader;\n\n// Removed - Spring Boot ServletInitializer not needed in Quarkus\n```\n\n## 3. ApplicationProps.java (support/ApplicationProps.java)\nReplace Spring's @ConfigurationProperties with Quarkus approach. Replace the full content with:\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.support;\n\nimport jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;\nimport org.eclipse.microprofile.config.inject.ConfigProperty;\n\n@ApplicationScoped\npublic class ApplicationProps {\n    @ConfigProperty(name = \"daytrader.max-quotes\", defaultValue = \"1000\")\n    int maxQuotes;\n\n    @ConfigProperty(name = \"daytrader.max-users\", defaultValue = \"500\")\n    int maxUsers;\n\n    public int getMaxQuotes() { return maxQuotes; }\n    public void setMaxQuotes(int maxQuotes) { this.maxQuotes = maxQuotes; }\n    public int getMaxUsers() { return maxUsers; }\n    public void setMaxUsers(int maxUsers) { this.maxUsers = maxUsers; }\n}\n```\n\n## 4. AsyncConfig.java (config/AsyncConfig.java)\nReplace Spring @Configuration/@Bean with CDI producers:\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.config;\n\nimport java.util.concurrent.ExecutorService;\nimport java.util.concurrent.Executors;\nimport java.util.concurrent.ScheduledExecutorService;\nimport java.util.concurrent.ThreadFactory;\n\nimport jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;\nimport jakarta.enterprise.inject.Produces;\nimport jakarta.inject.Named;\nimport jakarta.inject.Singleton;\n\n@ApplicationScoped\npublic class AsyncConfig {\n\n    @Produces\n    @Named(\"ManagedExecutorService\")\n    @Singleton\n    public ExecutorService managedExecutorService() {\n        return Executors.newCachedThreadPool(r -> {\n            Thread t = new Thread(r);\n            t.setName(\"mes-\" + t.getId());\n            t.setDaemon(true);\n            return t;\n        });\n    }\n\n    @Produces\n    @Named(\"ManagedScheduledTaskExecutor\")\n    @Singleton\n    public ScheduledExecutorService taskScheduler() {\n        return Executors.newScheduledThreadPool(4, r -> {\n            Thread t = new Thread(r);\n            t.setName(\"mstex-\" + t.getId());\n            t.setDaemon(true);\n            return t;\n        });\n    }\n\n    @Produces\n    @Named(\"ManagedThreadFactory\")\n    @Singleton\n    public ThreadFactory managedThreadFactoryBean() {\n        return Thread\n                .ofPlatform()\n                .name(\"mes-\", 0)\n                .uncaughtExceptionHandler((t, e) -> {\n                    System.err.println(\"Uncaught in \" + t.getName());\n                    e.printStackTrace();\n                })\n                .factory();\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## 5. JmsConfig.java (config/JmsConfig.java)\nReplace with a stub since we won't have a full JMS broker in Quarkus:\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.config;\n\n// JMS configuration - JMS functionality is disabled in Quarkus migration.\n// The JMS listeners are replaced with no-op stubs.\npublic class JmsConfig {\n}\n```\n\n## 6. WebSocketEndpointConfig.java (config/WebSocketEndpointConfig.java)\nReplace with:\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.config;\n\n// WebSocket endpoint configuration.\n// In Quarkus, @ServerEndpoint annotated classes are automatically discovered.\n// No explicit ServerEndpointExporter bean is needed.\npublic class WebSocketEndpointConfig {\n}\n```\n\n## 7. DualPortConfig.java (config/DualPortConfig.java)  \nReplace with:\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.config;\n\n// Dual port configuration is not needed in Quarkus.\n// Quarkus HTTP port is configured via application.properties.\npublic class DualPortConfig {\n}\n```\n\n## 8. ExecutorConfig.java (config/ExecutorConfig.java)\nKeep as-is (already empty).\n\n## 9. SpringEndpointConfigurator.java (web/SpringEndpointConfigurator.java)\nReplace with CDI-based:\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.web;\n\nimport jakarta.websocket.server.ServerEndpointConfig;\nimport jakarta.enterprise.inject.spi.CDI;\n\npublic class SpringEndpointConfigurator extends ServerEndpointConfig.Configurator {\n\n    @Override\n    public <T> T getEndpointInstance(Class<T> endpointClass) throws InstantiationException {\n        try {\n            return CDI.current().select(endpointClass).get();\n        } catch (Exception e) {\n            try {\n                return endpointClass.getDeclaredConstructor().newInstance();\n            } catch (Exception ex) {\n                throw new InstantiationException(ex.getMessage());\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## 10. TradeSLSBBean.java (impl/ejb3/TradeSLSBBean.java)\nThis is a big file. Replace all Spring annotations:\n- `@Service(\"Full EJB3\")` -> `@ApplicationScoped` + `@Named(\"Full EJB3\")`\n- `@Autowired` -> `@Inject`  \n- `@Transactional` (Spring) -> `@Transactional` (Jakarta)\n- `@Transactional(propagation = Propagation.REQUIRES_NEW)` -> `@Transactional(Transactional.TxType.REQUIRES_NEW)`\n- `@PersistenceContext` -> `@Inject`\n- Remove `org.springframework.*` imports\n- Add `jakarta.inject.Inject`, `jakarta.inject.Named`, `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped`\n- Remove JmsTemplate usages - replace with no-op logging (since we don't have embedded JMS in Quarkus)\n- Remove `import org.springframework.jms.core.JmsTemplate;`\n- Remove `import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;`\n- Remove `import org.springframework.stereotype.Service;`\n- Remove `import org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Propagation;`\n- Change `import org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional;` to `import jakarta.transaction.Transactional;`\n- For `queueOrder()`: Replace JmsTemplate send with a log message and call completeOrder directly (synchronous fallback)\n- For `publishQuotePriceChange()`: Replace JmsTemplate send with a log message (no-op)\n- Change `@Autowired private ConnectionFactory connectionFactory;` to remove it (no JMS)\n\n## 11. MarketSummarySingleton.java (impl/ejb3/MarketSummarySingleton.java)\n- `@Service` -> `@ApplicationScoped`\n- `@Autowired` -> `@Inject`\n- `@PersistenceContext` -> `@Inject`\n- `@Scheduled(cron = \"*/20 * * * * *\")` -> `@io.quarkus.scheduler.Scheduled(every = \"20s\")`\n- Remove Spring `ApplicationEventPublisher` - replace with CDI `jakarta.enterprise.event.Event`\n- Remove `org.springframework.*` imports\n- The `updateMarketSummary()` method needs to be public (not private) for Quarkus scheduler\n- Use `@Transactional` from `jakarta.transaction.Transactional`\n\n## 12. AsyncScheduledOrder.java (impl/ejb3/AsyncScheduledOrder.java)\n- `@Component` -> `@Dependent` (from `jakarta.enterprise.context.Dependent`)\n- `@Scope(\"prototype\")` -> removed (Dependent is Quarkus/CDI equivalent of prototype)  \n- `@Autowired` -> `@Inject`\n- Remove Spring imports\n\n## 13. AsyncScheduledOrderSubmitter.java (impl/ejb3/AsyncScheduledOrderSubmitter.java)\n- `@Component` -> `@ApplicationScoped`\n- `@RequestScope` -> Remove (not needed)\n- `@Autowired` -> `@Inject`\n- Replace `TaskScheduler` with `ScheduledExecutorService`\n- Remove Spring imports\n- Replace `mes.schedule(asyncOrder, Instant.now().plusMillis(500))` with `mes.schedule(asyncOrder, 500, TimeUnit.MILLISECONDS)`\n\n## 14. TradeDirect.java (impl/direct/TradeDirect.java)\n- `@Service(\"Direct (JDBC)\")` -> `@ApplicationScoped` + `@Named(\"Direct (JDBC)\")`\n- `@Autowired` -> `@Inject`\n- Remove `@Autowired(required = false)` for UserTransaction -> `@Inject` (it will be available in Quarkus)\n- Replace Spring `ApplicationEventPublisher` with CDI `Event`\n- Replace `JmsTemplate` usages in `queueOrder()` and `publishQuotePriceChange()` with no-op/logging\n- Remove `org.springframework.*` imports\n- Add CDI imports\n\n## 15. TradeDirectDBUtils.java (impl/direct/TradeDirectDBUtils.java)\n- `@Service` -> `@ApplicationScoped`\n- `@Autowired` -> `@Inject`\n- Remove Spring imports\n\n## 16. AsyncOrder.java (impl/direct/AsyncOrder.java)\n- `@Component` + `@Scope(\"prototype\")` -> `@Dependent`\n- `@Autowired(required = false)` -> `@Inject`\n- `@Inject @TradeJDBC TradeServices tradeService;` - keep as-is (already using jakarta.inject.Inject)\n- Remove Spring imports\n\n## 17. AsyncOrderSubmitter.java (impl/direct/AsyncOrderSubmitter.java)\n- `@Component` -> `@ApplicationScoped`\n- `@Autowired @Qualifier(\"ManagedExecutorService\")` -> `@Inject @Named(\"ManagedExecutorService\")`\n- Replace `ObjectFactory<AsyncOrder>` with `jakarta.enterprise.inject.Instance<AsyncOrder>`\n- Replace `asyncOrderFactory.getObject()` with `asyncOrderFactory.get()`\n- Remove Spring imports\n\n## 18. DTBroker3Listener.java (jms/DTBroker3Listener.java)\nReplace with a no-op stub since JMS is not available:\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.jms;\n\nimport jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;\nimport com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.util.Log;\n\n@ApplicationScoped\npublic class DTBroker3Listener {\n    // JMS listener disabled in Quarkus migration - no embedded Artemis available\n    // In Spring, this listened on \"TradeBrokerQueue\"\n    public void onBrokerQueueMessage(Object message) {\n        Log.trace(\"DTBroker3Listener: JMS disabled in Quarkus migration\");\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## 19. DTStreamer3Listener.java (jms/DTStreamer3Listener.java)\nReplace with a no-op stub:\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.jms;\n\nimport jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;\nimport com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.util.Log;\n\n@ApplicationScoped\npublic class DTStreamer3Listener {\n    // JMS listener disabled in Quarkus migration - no embedded Artemis available\n    // In Spring, this listened on \"TradeStreamerTopic\"\n    public void onStreamerTopicEvent(Object message) {\n        Log.trace(\"DTStreamer3Listener: JMS disabled in Quarkus migration\");\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## 20. DirectSLSBBean.java (impl/session2direct/DirectSLSBBean.java)\n- `@Service(\"Session to Direct\")` -> `@ApplicationScoped` + `@Named(\"Session to Direct\")`\n- Already using `@Inject` (jakarta), keep that\n- `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` is already correct\n- Remove `org.springframework.stereotype.Service` import\n\n## 21. RecentQuotePriceChangeList.java (util/RecentQuotePriceChangeList.java)\n- `@Component` -> `@ApplicationScoped`\n- Replace Spring `ApplicationEventPublisher` with CDI `Event`\n- `@Autowired` -> `@Inject`\n- Remove Spring imports\n\n## 22. events/QuotePriceChangeEvent.java, MarketSummaryUpdateEvent.java, HitEvent.java, HitAsyncEvent.java\nKeep as-is if they are simple records/class