{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01EDBspcMgLodRgiyp5wnvnJ","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully completed the migration of all the key Java source files from Spring Boot to Quarkus. Let me provide you with a comprehensive summary of all the changes made:\n\n## Summary of Quarkus Migration Changes\n\nI have successfully refactored all Java source files in the DayTrader application to replace Spring-specific annotations and patterns with Quarkus/CDI equivalents. Here's a detailed summary of the changes:\n\n### **Configuration and Main Classes**\n\n1. **DaytraderApplication.java** - Replaced Spring Boot main class with Quarkus main class using `@QuarkusMain` and `io.quarkus.runtime.Quarkus.run()`\n\n2. **ServletInitializer.java** - Removed Spring Boot ServletInitializer (not needed in Quarkus)\n\n3. **ApplicationProps.java** - Replaced `@ConfigurationProperties` with `@ApplicationScoped` and `@ConfigProperty` from MicroProfile Config\n\n4. **AsyncConfig.java** - Replaced Spring `@Configuration/@Bean` with CDI `@Produces` and changed to use standard Java `ExecutorService` and `ScheduledExecutorService`\n\n5. **JmsConfig.java** - Replaced with stub (JMS functionality disabled in Quarkus migration)\n\n6. **WebSocketEndpointConfig.java** - Replaced with stub (Quarkus auto-discovers WebSocket endpoints)\n\n7. **DualPortConfig.java** - Replaced with stub (port configuration via application.properties in Quarkus)\n\n8. **SpringEndpointConfigurator.java** - Replaced Spring ApplicationContext with CDI `CDI.current()`\n\n### **Core Implementation Classes**\n\n9. **TradeSLSBBean.java** - Major changes:\n   - `@Service` → `@ApplicationScoped` + `@Named`\n   - `@Autowired` → `@Inject`\n   - `@PersistenceContext` → `@Inject`\n   - `@Transactional(propagation = Propagation.REQUIRES_NEW)` → `@Transactional(Transactional.TxType.REQUIRES_NEW)`\n   - Removed JMS ConnectionFactory and JmsTemplate usage\n   - Replaced `queueOrder()` JMS send with synchronous call to `completeOrder()`\n   - Replaced `publishQuotePriceChange()` JMS send with logging (no-op)\n   - Replaced `pingTwoPhase()` JMS send with logging\n\n10. **MarketSummarySingleton.java**:\n    - `@Service` → `@ApplicationScoped`\n    - `@Autowired` → `@Inject`\n    - `@PersistenceContext` → `@Inject`\n    - `@Scheduled(cron = \"*/20 * * * * *\")` → `@Scheduled(every = \"20s\")` (Quarkus scheduler)\n    - Replaced Spring `ApplicationEventPublisher` with CDI `Event`\n    - Changed `publishEvent()` to `fire()`\n    - Made `updateMarketSummary()` method public (required for Quarkus scheduler)\n\n11. **AsyncScheduledOrder.java**:\n    - `@Component` + `@Scope(\"prototype\")` → `@Dependent`\n    - `@Autowired` → `@Inject`\n\n12. **AsyncScheduledOrderSubmitter.java**:\n    - `@Component` + `@RequestScope` → `@ApplicationScoped`\n    - `@Autowired` → `@Inject` + `@Named`\n    - Replaced Spring `TaskScheduler` with `ScheduledExecutorService`\n    - Changed `schedule(asyncOrder, Instant.now().plusMillis(500))` to `schedule(asyncOrder, 500, TimeUnit.MILLISECONDS)`\n\n### **Direct Implementation Classes**\n\n13. **TradeDirect.java**:\n    - `@Service` → `@ApplicationScoped` + `@Named`\n    - `@Autowired` → `@Inject`\n    - `@Autowired(required = false)` → `@Inject` (UserTransaction available in Quarkus)\n    - Replaced Spring `ApplicationEventPublisher` with CDI `Event`\n    - Changed `publishEvent()` to `fire()`\n    - Replaced `queueOrder()` JMS send with synchronous call to `completeOrder()`\n    - Replaced `publishQuotePriceChange()` JMS send with logging (no-op)\n\n14. **TradeDirectDBUtils.java**:\n    - `@Service` → `@ApplicationScoped`\n    - `@Autowired` → `@Inject`\n\n15. **AsyncOrder.java (direct)**:\n    - `@Component` + `@Scope(\"prototype\")` → `@Dependent`\n    - `@Autowired(required = false)` → `@Inject`\n\n16. **AsyncOrderSubmitter.java (direct)**:\n    - `@Component` → `@ApplicationScoped`\n    - `@Autowired` + `@Qualifier` → `@Inject` + `@Named`\n    - Replaced Spring `ObjectFactory` with CDI `Instance`\n    - Changed `getObject()` to `get()`\n\n### **JMS Listener Classes**\n\n17. **DTBroker3Listener.java** - Replaced with no-op stub (JMS disabled in Quarkus migration)\n\n18. **DTStreamer3Listener.java** - Replaced with no-op stub (JMS disabled in Quarkus migration)\n\n### **Session to Direct Classes**\n\n19. **DirectSLSBBean.java**:\n    - `@Service` → `@ApplicationScoped` + `@Named`\n    - Already using `@Inject` (jakarta), kept that\n    - Removed Spring imports\n\n### **Utility Classes**\n\n20. **RecentQuotePriceChangeList.java**:\n    - `@Component` → `@ApplicationScoped`\n    - Replaced Spring `ApplicationEventPublisher` with CDI `Event`\n    - `@Autowired` → `@Inject`\n    - Changed `publishEvent()` to `fire()`\n\n### **Key Migration Patterns Applied**\n\n- **Dependency Injection**: `@Autowired` → `@Inject`\n- **Component Scanning**: `@Service/@Component` → `@ApplicationScoped`\n- **Named Beans**: `@Service(\"name\")` → `@Named(\"name\")`\n- **Prototype Scope**: `@Scope(\"prototype\")` → `@Dependent`\n- **Event Publishing**: Spring `ApplicationEventPublisher.publishEvent()` → CDI `Event.fire()`\n- **Scheduled Tasks**: Spring `@Scheduled(cron)` → Quarkus `@Scheduled(every)`\n- **Transactions**: Spring `@Transactional(propagation)` → Jakarta `@Transactional(TxType)`\n- **Configuration**: `@ConfigurationProperties` → `@ConfigProperty`\n- **Bean Production**: `@Bean` → `@Produces`\n- **JMS**: Removed all JMS functionality (JmsTemplate, listeners) and replaced with synchronous calls or no-ops\n\nAll files have been successfully migrated to use Quarkus/CDI/Jakarta EE annotations and patterns instead of Spring-specific ones. The JMS functionality has been disabled as requested since there's no embedded Artemis in this Quarkus migration."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"56efa089-e1a8-4ed6-8ae5-0ef3f5d72aa6","uuid":"be992d03-5d39-4e62-8356-9c84e419b627"}
