{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01C4rHrSENVkJTK5Et1dATLG","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Summary\n\nI have successfully completed the migration of ALL remaining Spring imports across the DayTrader application to Quarkus/CDI equivalents. Here's a comprehensive summary of the changes made:\n\n### Files Changed (70 files total)\n\n#### **Interface Files (2 files)**\n1. **TradeEJB.java** - Replaced `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Qualifier` with `jakarta.inject.Qualifier`\n2. **TradeJDBC.java** - Replaced `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Qualifier` with `jakarta.inject.Qualifier`\n\n#### **Core Servlet Files (10 files)**\n3. **TradeWebContextListener.java** - Replaced Spring `Environment` and `ResourceLoader` with MicroProfile Config and Thread.currentThread().getContextClassLoader()\n4. **TradeServletAction.java** - Complex migration: removed `@Component`, `@SessionScope`, `@Autowired`, replaced `ApplicationContext` with CDI `Instance<TradeServices>` for dynamic bean lookup\n5. **MarketSummaryWebSocket.java** - Replaced Spring with `@ApplicationScoped`, `@Inject`, and CDI `Instance<TradeServices>`\n6. **MarketSummaryWebSocketEvents.java** - Replaced `@Component`, `@Autowired`, `@EventListener`, `@Async` with `@ApplicationScoped`, `@Inject`, `@ObservesAsync`\n7. **OrdersAlertFilter.java** - Replaced Spring autowiring with CDI `@Inject` and `Instance<TradeServices>`\n8. **PrimFilter.java** - Removed `SpringBeanAutowiringSupport`\n9. **TestServlet.java** - Removed `@Component`, replaced Spring `ApplicationContext` with CDI `Instance<TradeServices>`\n10. **TradeAppServlet.java** - Removed `@Component` and `SpringBeanAutowiringSupport`\n11. **TradeConfigServlet.java** - Removed `@Component` and `SpringBeanAutowiringSupport`\n12. **TradeScenarioServlet.java** - Removed `@Component` and `SpringBeanAutowiringSupport`\n\n#### **Managed Executor Servlets (3 files)**\n13. **PingManagedThread.java** - Replaced `@Component`, `@Autowired @Qualifier` with `@Inject @Named`, changed `AsyncTaskExecutor` to `ExecutorService`\n14. **PingManagedExecutor.java** - Replaced `@Component`, constructor injection with `@Inject @Named`, changed `AsyncTaskExecutor` to `ExecutorService`\n15. **PingWebSocketJson.java** - Replaced `@Component`, `@Autowired @Qualifier` with `@ApplicationScoped`, `@Inject @Named`, changed `TaskExecutor` to `ExecutorService`\n\n#### **Special Case Files (5 files)**\n16. **PingJDBCRead.java** - Replaced `@Autowired ApplicationContext` with CDI `Instance<TradeServices>` lookup\n17. **CDIMethodConstraintBean.java** - Replaced `@RequestScope` with `@RequestScoped`\n18. **PingServlet2MDBQueue.java** - Removed JMS functionality (disabled in Quarkus migration), removed `@Autowired ConnectionFactory` and `JmsTemplate`\n19. **PingServlet2MDBTopic.java** - Removed JMS functionality (disabled in Quarkus migration), removed `@Autowired ConnectionFactory` and `JmsTemplate`\n20. **CDIEventProducer.java** - Replaced Spring `ApplicationEventPublisher` with CDI `Event<T>`, added `@ApplicationScoped`, replaced `@Qualifier` with `@Named`\n\n#### **CDI Prims Servlets (5 files)**\n21. **PingServletBeanValCDI.java** - Replaced `@Autowired` with `@Inject`\n22. **PingCDIBean.java** - Replaced `@RequestScope` with `@RequestScoped`\n23. **PingServletCDI.java** - Replaced `@Autowired` with `@Inject`\n24. **PingServletCDIBeanManagerViaCDICurrent.java** - Replaced `@Autowired` with `@Inject`, removed broken init code\n25. **PingServletCDIBeanManagerViaJNDI.java** - Replaced `@Autowired` with `@Inject`, removed broken init code\n\n#### **All Other Prims Servlets (45+ files)**\n- Batch removed `@Component` annotations\n- Batch removed `SpringBeanAutowiringSupport.processInjectionBasedOnServletContext()` and `processInjectionBasedOnCurrentContext()` calls\n- Removed simple Spring imports across all prims servlets in subdirectories (drive, ejb3, http2, beanval, cdi)\n\n### Key Migration Patterns Applied\n\n1. **Import Replacements:**\n   - `org.springframework.stereotype.Component` → REMOVED (servlets use `@WebServlet`, CDI beans use `@ApplicationScoped`)\n   - `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired` → `jakarta.inject.Inject`\n   - `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Qualifier` → `jakarta.inject.Named` or `jakarta.inject.Qualifier`\n   - `org.springframework.web.context.annotation.SessionScope` → REMOVED\n   - `org.springframework.web.context.annotation.RequestScope` → `jakarta.enterprise.context.RequestScoped`\n   - `org.springframework.context.ApplicationContext` → `jakarta.enterprise.inject.Instance<T>`\n   - `org.springframework.context.ApplicationEventPublisher` → `jakarta.enterprise.event.Event<T>`\n   - `org.springframework.context.event.EventListener` → `jakarta.enterprise.event.Observes` / `@ObservesAsync`\n   - `org.springframework.scheduling.annotation.Async` → REMOVED (use ExecutorService directly)\n   - `org.springframework.core.task.AsyncTaskExecutor` / `TaskExecutor` → `java.util.concurrent.ExecutorService`\n   - `org.springframework.core.env.Environment` → MicroProfile Config `ConfigProvider`\n   - `org.springframework.core.io.ResourceLoader` → `Thread.currentThread().getContextClassLoader()`\n   - `org.springframework.jms.core.JmsTemplate` → REMOVED (JMS disabled)\n\n2. **Annotation Replacements:**\n   - `@Component` → REMOVED or `@ApplicationScoped`\n   - `@Autowired` → `@Inject`\n   - `@Qualifier(\"...\")` → `@Named(\"...\")`\n   - `@SessionScope` → REMOVED (manual session management)\n   - `@RequestScope` → `@RequestScoped`\n   - `@EventListener` → `@Observes` / `@ObservesAsync`\n   - `@Async` → REMOVED\n\n3. **Code Pattern Replacements:**\n   - `SpringBeanAutowiringSupport.processInjectionBasedOnServletContext()` → REMOVED (CDI injection automatic)\n   - `applicationContext.getBean(key, TradeServices.class)` → CDI `Instance<TradeServices>` iteration with custom `getBeanName()` method\n   - Spring event publishing → CDI `Event.fire()` / `Event.fireAsync()`\n   - JMS operations → Disabled with message to user\n\n### Verification\n\n- **0 remaining Spring imports** - Verified with grep across entire src/main/java directory\n- **140 total Java files** in the project\n- **70 files modified** to remove Spring dependencies\n\nAll Spring Boot annotations and imports have been successfully migrated to Quarkus/CDI equivalents while maintaining the application's functionality."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"56efa089-e1a8-4ed6-8ae5-0ef3f5d72aa6","uuid":"df8488ee-7dc0-4430-80bd-2a44f7aed5a9"}
