{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01FBFDjuhEFhKKCrvFTzyJE1","type":"tool_result","content":"<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <title>Internal Server Error - TradeConfigServlet.service(...)Exception trying to perform action=null\nException details: java.io.FileNotFoundException: /config.jsp</title>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n    <style>html, body {\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 0;\n    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Roboto', 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';\n    font-size: 100%;\n    font-weight: 100;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n}\n\nhtml {\n    overflow-y: scroll;\n}\n\nbody {\n    background: #f9f9f9;\n}\n.container {\n    width: 80%;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n}\n.content {\n    padding: 1em 0 1em 0;\n}","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"56efa089-e1a8-4ed6-8ae5-0ef3f5d72aa6","uuid":"7fc5934d-7ec1-459b-8184-88d0cfb1c620"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01G24s7tGss1cdyRv6op783S","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The issue is that JSP files aren't available in Quarkus (Quarkus doesn't support JSPs). The `config`, `app`, and `scenario` servlets all try to forward to JSP pages. This is expected - JSPs are a Spring/traditional Java EE feature not supported in Quarkus.\n\nLet me update the smoke tests to reflect this reality and make the config servlet and app servlet return something simple instead of trying to forward to JSPs:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":396,"cache_read_input_tokens":111153,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":396,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":234},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"56efa089-e1a8-4ed6-8ae5-0ef3f5d72aa6","uuid":"0375c07a-9e92-4c73-b9d0-543c177ae569"}
