{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_0114BexLJ4gqE4xkTgGMDGzq","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The migration is complete. Here's the final report:\n\n---\n\n### Migration Summary\n\n- **Frameworks:** Spring Boot 3.3.0 → Quarkus 3.15.1\n- **Overall outcome:** SUCCESS - Application builds, runs, and passes all 4 smoke tests\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Replaced Spring Boot parent/dependencies with Quarkus BOM and extensions\n- Dockerfile: Changed CMD from spring-boot:run to quarkus:dev\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Rewritten for Quarkus configuration\n- src/main/resources/application.yml: Cleared (all config in .properties)\n- src/main/resources/import.sql: Changed INSERT to MERGE to avoid duplicates\n- src/main/java/.../DaytraderApplication.java: @SpringBootApplication -> @QuarkusMain\n- src/main/java/.../ServletInitializer.java: Removed Spring-specific content\n- src/main/java/.../support/ApplicationProps.java: @ConfigurationProperties -> @ConfigProperty\n- src/main/java/.../config/AsyncConfig.java: @Configuration/@Bean -> @ApplicationScoped/@Produces\n- src/main/java/.../config/JmsConfig.java: Stub (JMS disabled)\n- src/main/java/.../config/WebSocketEndpointConfig.java: Stub (auto-discovery)\n- src/main/java/.../config/DualPortConfig.java: Stub\n- src/main/java/.../web/SpringEndpointConfigurator.java: CDI.current() instead of Spring\n- src/main/java/.../impl/ejb3/TradeSLSBBean.java: Full EJB3 service -> CDI\n- src/main/java/.../impl/ejb3/MarketSummarySingleton.java: @Scheduled -> Quarkus @Scheduled\n- src/main/java/.../impl/ejb3/AsyncScheduledOrder.java: CDI Instance lookup\n- src/main/java/.../impl/ejb3/AsyncScheduledOrderSubmitter.java: CDI + ScheduledExecutorService\n- src/main/java/.../impl/direct/TradeDirect.java: CDI Event, no JMS\n- src/main/java/.../impl/direct/TradeDirectDBUtils.java: @ApplicationScoped\n- src/main/java/.../impl/direct/AsyncOrder.java